Nigerian music star and entertainer, Harrison Tare Okiri popularly known as Harrysong, has officially proposed to his long-time lover, Isioma. Harrysong broke the news on Instagram on Wednesday with a video of his girlfriend wearing the ring. He said he had found a mother and a wife in her, after he lost his mother many years ago. “I lost my mother when I was very young, I’m happy to have found a mother in you. “You care for me, you forgive me so easily, you make my life so beautiful. “You’re patient and kind. “What a beauty to behold. “You’re my #Isioma,” he wrote. See Video:   I lost my mother when I was very young, I’m happy to have found a mother in you You care for me, you forgive me so easily, you make my life so beautiful You’re patient and kind. What a beauty to behold You’re my #Isioma #KingIsi2020 #Isiomasaidyes A post shared by  KINGMAKER|| (@iamharrysong) on Jan 14, 2020 at 5:48am PST 